Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:48.62,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}跳出舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:53.92,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}燃烧似的风景
